# Keep the build context/image clean (CI builds from a fresh checkout with none of these).
# Without this, `COPY ops` / `COPY backend` would pull local virtualenvs (mac/arm64) into the
# linux image — bloat and wrong-arch binaries.
**/.venv
**/venv
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
.git
.claude
.cdk.out
**/cdk.out
